sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Người dùng (React)
    participant B as Backend (Spring Boot)
    participant GCS as Cloud Storage (Raw)
    participant CF as Cloud Function (Go)
    participant V as Vision API
    participant R as Redis Pub/Sub

    U->>B: POST /files/upload
    B->>GCS: Upload ảnh lên bucket
    GCS-->>B: Hoàn tất
    B-->>U: Trả về URL tạm thời
    
    GCS-)CF: Event Trigger: Object Finalize
    activate CF
    CF->>V: Gọi hàm DetectSafeSearch
    activate V
    V-->>CF: Kết quả (Adult, Violence...)
    deactivate V
    
    alt Có vi phạm
        CF->>GCS: Xoá ảnh khỏi bucket Raw
        CF->>R: Publish status="rejected"
    else An toàn
        CF->>GCS: Copy sang bucket Processed
        CF->>GCS: Xoá ảnh ở bucket Raw
        CF->>R: Publish status="processed"
    end
    deactivate CF
